🛠️ HOW TO INSTALL AND RUN CODEX

To install and run this tool:

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
✅ STEP 1: Open Terminal and go to the tool folder
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

cd /path/to/Codex4665

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
✅ STEP 2: Run the installer script
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

chmod +x install_codex.sh
./install_codex.sh

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
✅ STEP 3: Follow the instructions shown after installation
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

The installer will:

✔️ Create a virtual environment  
✔️ Install all required Python libraries  
✔️ Show you the final command to run CODEX  

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

🎉 That’s it! Just follow the instructions, and the tool will be ready to use.

